            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Ind</abbr><ex>ictione</ex></expan> III <lb n="2"/>Bon<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> memor<lb break="no" n="3"/>i<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> Liberatae <lb n="4"/>bixit <note>sic</note> annos <lb n="5"/>XL <expan><abbr>pl</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>inus</ex></expan> pa<lb break="no" n="6"/>uci et mali et <lb n="7"/>requiebit <note>sic</note> in <lb n="8"/><expan><ex>Christ</ex><abbr>o</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>men</abbr><ex>se</ex></expan> Iu<lb break="no" n="9"/>lio <abbr>com</abbr> VIII </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Audias in illa<lb break="no" n="2"/>die bocem D<expan><ex>omi</ex><abbr>ni</abbr></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><ex>Ies</ex><abbr>u</abbr></expan> <expan><ex>Christ</ex><abbr>i</abbr></expan> dicentis <lb n="4"/>remissa sunt <lb n="5"/>tibi unibersa <lb n="6"/>delicta
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Für die Inschrift wurden zwei Platten eines Pflasters wiederverwendet; sehr wahrscheinlich zusammengehörig. Fr. Fragment a: Z. 1(Anfang): Kreuzzeichnung; (Ende): Kreuzzeichnung. Fragment a: Z. 9: Datumangabe mit Stigma (= 6) wiedergegeben; Fragment b: Z. 6(Ende): Kreuzzeichnung.</p>
            </div>
